</head>
<body id="app-layout">
    <div class="container" id="headerContainer">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="pull-left col-xs-4 no-padding-left">
                <a class="navbar-brand" href="/" id="brandLink">stats.takepoint.io</a>
            </div>
            <div class="pull-right col-xs-8 col-sm-5 col-sm-offset-1 col-md-4 col-md-offset-2 col-lg-3 col-lg-offset-3 padding-right-8px">
                <div class="input-group" id="searchBox">
                    <input type="text" class="form-control" id="searchUsername" placeholder="Username" maxlength="12">
                    <span class="input-group-btn">
                        <button class="btn btn-default" type="button" onclick="search()" id="searchButton">Search</button>
                    </span>
                </div>      
                <script>
                    document.onkeydown = function(event){
                        if(event.keyCode == 13) {
                            search();
                        }
                    };

                    function search(){
                        var username = document.getElementById('searchUsername').value;
                        var currentBaseURL = window.location.href.split("/")[2];
                        document.location = '/user/' + username;
                    }
                </script>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
	<div class="container" id="pageContainer">
		<div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-12">
				<div class="container margin-bottom-20px">
					<h2 class="margin-bottom-15px">Description</h2>
					<p class="margin-right-30px-not-mobile"><b>Takepoint.io is a tactical, objective-based shooter. Capture and defend points from other teams, unlock weapons, upgrades and perks. Player stats can be viewed at stats.takepoint.io.</b></p>

					<h2 class="margin-bottom-15px">Controls</h2>
					<p class="margin-right-30px-not-mobile">Move: WASD or Arrow Keys
					<br>Shoot: Left Click
					<br>Reload: R
					<br>Use Perk: SPACE
					<br>Chat: ENTER
					</p>

					<h2 class="margin-bottom-15px">Health/Damage</h2>
					<p class="margin-right-30px-not-mobile">When you spawn and start taking damage, you'll see two HP bars. The orange one is a temporary shield, it'll absorb damage but it won't recharge. The green bar is your health, it will recharge over time.</p>
					<img id="classImage" src="/img/healthBars.jpg">

					<h2 class="margin-bottom-15px">Upgrades</h2>
					<p class="margin-right-30px-not-mobile">You'll receive ONE upgrade point at EACH LEVEL from 1 to 10. After level 10, you'll be awarded an upgrade point EVERY THREE LEVELS.</p>
					<img id="classImage" src="/img/upgradeSelection.jpg">

					<h2 class="margin-bottom-15px">Weapons</h2>
					<p class="margin-right-30px-not-mobile">These weapons are unlocked when you reach <b>LEVEL 10.</b> They will automatically replace your pistol. </p>
					<img id="classImage" src="/img/assault.jpg">
					<img id="classImage" src="/img/sniper.jpg">
					<img id="classImage" src="/img/shotgun.jpg">

					<h2 class="margin-bottom-15px">Perks</h2>
					<p class="margin-right-30px-not-mobile">These perks are unlocked when you reach <b>LEVEL 15.</b> Press SPACE to use them.</p>
					<img id="classImage" src="/img/health.jpg">
					<img id="classImage" src="/img/barrier.jpg">
					<img id="classImage" src="/img/gas.jpg">
					<img id="classImage" src="/img/frag.jpg">
					<img id="classImage" src="/img/selfDestruct.jpg">
					<img id="classImage" src="/img/turret.jpg">
					
					<h2 class="margin-bottom-15px">Social</h2>
					<a target="_blank" href="https://discord.gg/vbZqzuv">discord.gg/vbZqzuv</a><br>
					<p class="margin-right-30px-not-mobile">Our privacy policy is available <a href="/privacy">here.</a></p>

					<h2 class="margin-bottom-15px">Thumbnail</h2>
					<img src="/img/thumbnail.png" height="266" width="400">
				</div>
			</div>
        </div>
	</div>

    <div class="container">
        <footer class="footer navbar-fixed-bottom" id="footer">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-xs-6 margin-top-10px" style="text-align: left">
                        <p>Copyleft <a class="copyleft">&copy;</a> <%= new Date(Date.now()).getFullYear() %> takepoint.io. All rights reversed.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-xs-6 margin-top-10px" style="text-align: right">
                        <a class="plain-link" href="/about">About</a> | <a class="plain-link" href="/privacy">Privacy Policy</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </footer>
    </div>

